{"tid":650968,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Peppa Pig遭抖音封殺","createTime":"2018-05-02T18:51:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T12:17:42.000Z","uid":20058,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"ddb39e24ab60309ec97857bf5a0b365ea861c9af","tid":650968,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T18:51:01.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】英國卡通人物Peppa Pig在外國和中國都廣受歡迎，不過近日就遭到內地視頻平台「抖音」封殺。<br />\n<br />\n美國《紐約時報》報道，在過去的周末「抖音」上超過三萬條涉及Peppa Pig的短片都遭到刪除。到了星期二下午，甚至連「Peppa Pig」的搜尋標籤都被列入黑名單。<br />\n<br />\n英國的原創者最初是針對學前兒童創作「Peppa Pig」這個角色，有關卡通於2015年在內地首播後，這隻粉紅色的可愛小豬更逐漸成為內地社交平台的「網紅」。<br />\n<br />\n不過在近數個月，這隻本身形象正面的小豬被指跟一些反社會主流價值的年輕人劃上等號。有小學生和網民更模仿那些不務正業的人拍短片，又將「Peppa Pig」的貼紙貼在自己身上扮作紋身。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有關社會風氣引起官方媒體批評，《人民日報》上周四發表評論指，「Peppa Pig」引發的跟風熱潮對國內年輕人有不良影響，值得民眾警惕。<br />\n<br />\n《紐約時報》報道指，無證據顯示「抖音」是因應政府所下的命令封殺「Peppa Pig」，相信今次是「抖音」作出的自我審查措施。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=304375\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D304375&d=51RUcZDpF0N1ha8sYjMM%2FVeK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=051813d2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D304375&h=b6c7067b\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=304375</a>"},{"pid":"973eb95c2788fa8a75f4dbc6f0419250b2935642","tid":650968,"uid":41204,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T18:53:06.000Z","msg":"中國豬驚咗自己同類都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0555b963d977fa515290da60112d17aa0167e074","tid":650968,"uid":550,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T20:22:24.000Z","msg":"有喜羊羊就夠啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff574c1f19f52db02c680abd302f8b40f9eccca7","tid":650968,"ui